  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13108679/decemberhero-900x500.jpg" alt="DecemberHero" data-udi="umb://media/515d29aa89454b84888caf6df76ba1b0" /></p>
<h2>Lapland in December</h2>
<p>Why go on holiday to Lapland in December? </p>
<ul>
<li>Well of course - it's <a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks">Christmas</a>!</li>
<li>Enjoy the festive feel of Lapland during December, with resorts showcasing decorations, lights and of course a town square Christmas tree.</li>
<li>It's always worth finding time to explore the Christmas markets hosted in resorts during December - there are always tasty drinks and delicious drinks on offer, plus plenty of homemade crafts and gifts to purchase.</li>
<li>Don't forget to <a data-udi="umb://document/05d3b1900a534df49444693b1f18fdb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/05d3b1900a534df49444693b1f18fdb0}" title="Santa’s Elves Hideaway">visit Santa</a> if you are on holiday near <a data-udi="umb://document/180d7175a6584f82a5f54d14d7f8a34a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/180d7175a6584f82a5f54d14d7f8a34a}" title="A Santa experience family holiday">Christmas</a>.</li>
<li>Celebrate in style at New Years Eve and welcome in the new year watching earths own natural firework display (plus some man-made ones) of the <a data-udi="umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995}" title="Northern Lights">Northern Lights</a>. </li>
<li>Many of our December Lapland holidays include a Festive Feast around Christmas - look out for this when booking your holiday. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd}" title="Deals" class="c-btn">Lapland deals</a></p>
<p>Enjoy a range of fun excursions - Lapland offers everything from Husky sleigh rides, meeting reindeer, a days skiing to an overnight trip in a glass igloo. View all the available excursions: </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" class="c-btn">Lapland excursions</a></p>
<h3>Best resorts in Lapland during December </h3>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Muonio</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108734/muonionovember-900x500.jpg" alt="MuonioNovemver" data-udi="umb://media/017879a94e26450686b57a32f3ecd86e" /></p>
<ul>
<li>A hidden gem of a resort that not many know of - therefore making it the least commercialised of many Lapland resorts. </li>
<li>An exclusive resort for the festive period only.</li>
<li>An all-inclusive package holiday offer with Inghams that includes meeting Santa.</li>
<li>The resort is located near Lake Jerisjärv, the perfect location for spotting the Northern Lights.</li>
<li><strong>Best place to stay in Muonio - </strong><a data-udi="umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0bebfc4d25c141acaa0885b66699c486}" title="Jeris Lakeside Resort"><strong>The Jeris lakeside resort</strong></a> for the ideal winter escape. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13103585/dsc07998.jpg" alt="JerisResort" data-udi="umb://media/f77bb468f0c84ba394ccf50595ca8ec0" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi" class="c-btn">View Muonio resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Saariselka</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108682/saariselkadecember-500x330.jpg" alt="SaariselkaDecember" data-udi="umb://media/1a4308a78fff4a7d80264925a876062b" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Get all the family together out on the slopes in the snow and enjoy the longest toboggan run in Lapland.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka" class="c-btn">View Saariselka resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Yllas</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108683/yllasdecember-500x330.jpg" alt="YllasDecember" data-udi="umb://media/d8cac5b2baf647eead16f93da988c8be" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Enjoy a day trip to the Ice village to marvel at the hand-made ice sculptures and enjoy a drink in the Ice Bar. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas" class="c-btn">View Yllas resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Levi</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13108681/levidecember-500x330.jpg" alt="LeviDecember" data-udi="umb://media/6e988ffa5b734036905817b4c7407b66" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Book an overnight stay in one of the glass igloos to immerse yourself in the view of the Northern Lights.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi" class="c-btn">View Levi resort</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<h3>Best Lapland accommodation in December</h3>
<p>Here we have selected a highlighted accommodation option per the above resorts to give you an overview of the range of accommodation options you will find available in Lapland.</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Hotel Panorama</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi"><strong>Levi</strong></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13078685/hotel_levi_panorama_-_scenic_saunas_4_20170215_1323476313.jpg" alt="HotelPanorama" data-udi="umb://media/1718cf3daf3b4c96b9af45d8dcdf4b69" /></p>
<ul>
<li>This 4* Hotel and apartment offering showcases a sky bar with panoramic views.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1299bbf58ca94d4699c68f628cf93f89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1299bbf58ca94d4699c68f628cf93f89}" title="Panorama Hotel and Apartments" class="c-btn">View Hotel Panorama</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Wilderness Hotel</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka"><strong>Saariselka</strong></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13107161/wilderness_hotel_juutua_finland_dining_view.jpg" alt="WildernessHotel" data-udi="umb://media/ae2bd093da594600b367759f9e52eb4e" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Modern comfort with local charm, this hotel has stunning views over the Inari Lake.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/8972f5d06dd34c9a86a145441144cc82" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8972f5d06dd34c9a86a145441144cc82}" title="Juutua Arctic Aurora Adventure" class="c-btn">View Willderness hotel</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow ">
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Miilu Cabins</h4>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas"><strong>Yllas</strong></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13106629/miilu_northern_lights_cabins_yllas_exterior-1.jpg" alt="MiiluCabins" data-udi="umb://media/57f84f585caf4f669e29b0d6d187ff70" /></p>
<ul>
<li>These are delightful Finnish style cabins on the shoreline of Ylläsjärvi Lake. </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas" class="c-btn">View Miilu Cabins</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Lapland at Christmas</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13108672/christmas-900x550.jpg" alt="Christmas&amp;NYE" data-udi="umb://media/fefbbd30b946443ca4866b33eaaa2186" /></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/2372bbf47f2b40169a53b9b43d3145c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2372bbf47f2b40169a53b9b43d3145c2}" title="Lapland holidays at Christmas" class="c-btn" data-="">View Christmas and NYE</a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Travel, accommodation and transfers? We’ve got you covered. Book your holiday online or give us a call. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel with confidence </h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
